        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/164/209",
        "text": [
          "١٦٤. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مَنْ قَضَى حَقَّ مَنْ لَا يَقْضِي حَقَّهُ فَقَدْ عَبَدَهُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "164. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: He who fulfils the right of a man who does not fulfil his right, (is as though he) worships him."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
